  <h1>Welcome to SAFE Scholars!</h1>
  <h2>What is SAFE?</h2>
  <p>This is a resource hub whose mission is to find the latest resources targeted towards first-gen low income students to help combat against underfunding in our communities. The acronym SAFE meaning "Supporting Achievement and Futures for Everyone"</p>

  
  <h3>Resources Include:</h3>  
    <ul>
      <li>Scholarship Search</li>
      <li>Online Advocacy Community</li>
      <li>Local Resource Database</li>
      <li>Personalized College Roadmaps</li>
      <li>Regular Updates on Educational News</li>
    </ul>

  <h3>The Story</h3>
  <p>The idea for SAFE Scholars was born out of a desire to find a resource hub to help combat the lack of funding in schools starting in the States of Texas, and eventually, nationwide!</p>

